              <p class="style2"><a name="19"></a>18.
                For examples of the various slants offered, see  Updegrove, Andrew, &quot;Spin Sets in on Internet Governance Compromise ,&quot;  the Standards Blog, November 18, 2005, ConsortiumInfo.org, at &lt;  <a href="http://www.consortiuminfo.org/newsblog/blog.php?ID=1751">http://www.consortiuminfo.org/newsblog/blog.php?ID=1751</a>&gt;.</p>
