                                        <tr>
                                          <td width="560" valign="top" bgcolor="#C4EECE" class="style2"><em> <strong> </strong></em>
                                              <p class="style111"><strong><em>Consortium futures trend upwards: </em></strong><em> This years rate of new-consortium formation has been noticeably lower than over the last two years  a trend that was reversed in recent weeks as a healthy crop of new organizations was launched in the areas of mobile Linux, security and processors.</em> </p></td>
