                                          <td colspan="2"><p><strong><em>It's a tactical move by Microsoft to give its  proprietary document formats a glimmer of openness</em></strong><em> [November 23, 2005]</em></p></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="style2">
                                          <td width="200" height="45"><p>&nbsp;</p></td>
                                          <td width="333"><p>Ovum Research Director Gary  Barnett<a href="http://uk.builder.com/0,39026540,39284979,00.htm">...Full Story</a></p>                                            
