                                      <table width="577" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                        <tr class="style2">
                                          <td colspan="2"><p><em><strong>We  are proud that our licensing program has enabled many new entrants to design  innovative wireless devices and compete in the 3G marketplace </strong>[November 6,  2005]</em></p></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="style2">
                                          <td width="200" height="30"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>
                                          <td width="333"><p class="style2">Qualcomm  CEO Dr. Paul E. Jacobs, denying allegations made to the EC<a href="http://www.itnewsonline.com/showstory.php?storyid=1640&scatid=8&contid=4">...Full  Story</a></p></td>
                                        </tr>
